OL,3,CAbbotsford House giving visitors
OL,4,Cchance to experience Christmas in the
OL,5,C1820s
OL,7,FThe historic Borders home of Sir
OL,8,FWalter Scott is giving people a
OL,9,Fglimpse into how Scott and his family
OL,10,Fwould've celebrated the festive period
OL,11,F200 years ago.
OL,13,FHe's one of the country's most famous
OL,14,Fwriters and built his home near
OL,15,FMelrose, overlooking the River Tweed,
OL,16,Fin the early 1800s.
OL,18,FNow, those who look after the house
OL,19,Fhave decided to take visitors back to
OL,20,FScott's first Christmas there in 1823.
