OL,5,C1820s
OL,7,FScott's own writings have given those
OL,8,Fcurating this experience a wealth of
OL,9,Fknowledge on what it it would've been
OL,10,Flike.
OL,12,F"He and his wife Charlotte would've
OL,13,Farrived here (from Edinburgh) on
OL,14,FChristmas Eve which also happened to
OL,15,Fbe their wedding anniversary and they
OL,16,Fwould've spent the next 12 days
OL,17,Fcelebrating with their friends
OL,18,Fculminating in a winter ball on the
OL,19,F5th January in the library."
