OL,5,C1820s
OL,7,FThe dining table is set as it would've
OL,8,Fbeen back then with place settings for
OL,9,Ffriends and family from all over the
OL,10,FBorders.
OL,12,FClaudia said that for Scott, it was
OL,13,Fthe more the merrier.
OL,15,F"He would have more than twenty people
OL,16,Fsitting in the dining room and some of
OL,17,Fhis employees would join too, he was
OL,18,Fhappy to have as many people as he
OL,19,Fcould around him at Christmas.
