OL,3,CAbbotsford House giving visitors
OL,4,Cchance to experience Christmas in the
OL,5,C1820s
OL,7,F"They always had goose on Christmas
OL,8,Fday, spiced punch, mulled wine and
OL,9,FChristmas cake."
OL,11,FAnd where else would you expect to see
OL,12,Fa Christmas Tree constructed from more
OL,13,Fthan 250 books but Abbotsford House.
OL,15,FThe Waverley Tree is the main
OL,16,Fattraction set in the bay window of
OL,17,FScott's vast library.
OL,19,FTours of Scott's Christmas are
OL,20,Favailable to the public every day from
OL,21,Fnow until 31st December.
